          <div class="cmd-row"><span class="cmd cmd-jenkins">post { unstable { ... } }</span><span class="desc">Run if tests failed but build passed</span></div>
          <div class="cmd-row"><span class="cmd cmd-jenkins">post { changed { ... } }</span><span class="desc">Run if result changed from previous build</span></div>
